One of the more popular conspiracy theories about the origins of coronavirus is that it is a bioweapon developed by the Chinese in the Wuhan Virology Institute.
One of the most serious effects the coronavirus pandemic has had on the world is the near shutdown of global trade.
(RELATED: As Coronavirus Spreads, Most Of America’s Medicine Still Comes From China)Already, Chinese exports have slumped.
If coronavirus was a bioweapon, its country of origin would be one of the hardest hit economically because of the massive hit to global trade.
Given the effects the virus has had on China’s projects, it makes little to no sense for the Chinese government to create a bioweapon like coronavirus, much less release it.